text: Bridgeton Historic District is located in Bridgeton, Cumberland County, New Jersey. The district was added to the National Register of Historic Places on October 29, 1982. ==See also== *National Register of Historic Places listings in Cumberland County, New Jersey ==References== The Davis House on Commerce Street, c. 1855-1866 Category:Bridgeton, New Jersey Category:Historic districts on the National Register of Historic Places in New Jersey Category:Houses on the National Register of Historic Places in New Jersey Category:Geography of Cumberland County, New Jersey Category:National Register of Historic Places in Cumberland County, New Jersey Category:Houses in Cumberland County, New Jersey Category:New Jersey Register of Historic Places
